The,X,Toolkit,XTK,is,a,lightweight,toolkit,for,visualizing,scientific,data,It,can,read,a,variety,of,formats,for,surface,models,volume,files,tractography,files,scalar,overlay,files,look,up,table,files,and,D,texture,files,XTK,can,perform,a,variety,of,operations,with,D,image,data,including,volume,rendering,thresholding,and,cross,sectional,slicing,It,also,provides,support,for,constructive,solid,geometry,label,maps,color,tables,and,surface,overlays,New,users,can,learn,to,use,XTK,by,looking,at,demos,or,following,along,with,the,lessons,provided,XTK,can,be,integrated,into,websites,using,JavaScript,code